title: Number of homicides in Sweden 2008 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of homicides. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
In general Number of homicides has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of homicides, about 113.0 was reported at Year 2017
The lowest Number of homicides, of value 68.0 was reported at Year 2012
